The following How To series will teach you the basics of Static Meshes and the Staic Mesh Editor.  From importing a mesh from an outside 3D modeling program, to setting up collsion to react with other objects in your level, to setting up sockets so that you can attach your mesh with another object in your scene, this How To series will help you get a better grasp on the Static Mesh Editor and feel more comfortable with every aspect of setting up Static Meshes to be used in your level.



